main event: A civilian in Kemah, Texas observed a spider web-like material floating down for a long while during Spring 1961.
interesting points: The material was seen drifting slowly 1-2 feet above the ground., The object made no sound or emitted any odors., Observers at the station watched the peculiar drifting object for several hours., There was no physical evidence collected from the sighting., The conclusion speculated it might be a UFO or an unidentified phenomenon.
